### IPL Franchise Store — API examples
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension or JetBrains HTTP client.
### Run the API first:  cd src/IplStore.Api ; dotnet run
### Base URL assumes the default Kestrel port below — adjust if yours differs.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5080/api/v1
@adminEmail = admin@iplstore.local
@adminPassword = Admin#12345
@customerEmail = fan@iplstore.local
@customerPassword = Fan#12345

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### AUTH
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newfan@example.com",
  "fullName": "New Fan",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}

###

# @name loginCustomer
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{customerEmail}}",
  "password": "{{customerPassword}}"
}

###
@customerToken = {{loginCustomer.response.body.accessToken}}
@refreshToken = {{loginCustomer.response.body.refreshToken}}

# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}

### Current user profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Refresh the access token (rotation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CATALOG (Requirement 1 & 2)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Product list (paginated + sortable)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=price&sortDir=asc

### Product details by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/mumbai-indians-home-jersey-2026

### Franchises (for filters / navigation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/franchises

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### SEARCH (Requirement 3) — by name, type, franchise + facets
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Free-text + franchise filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?q=jersey&franchise=MI

### Type + price range + stock filter, with facet counts in the response
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?type=Cap&minPrice=100&maxPrice=800&inStockOnly=true

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### CART (Requirement 4) — auth required
### Replace {{variantId}} with an id from a product details response.
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### View cart
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Add an item (use a real variant id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productVariantId": "REPLACE-WITH-VARIANT-ID",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Update a line quantity (0 removes it)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/cart/items/REPLACE-WITH-ITEM-ID
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "quantity": 1 }

### Remove a line
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/items/REPLACE-WITH-ITEM-ID
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Empty the cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### ORDERS & HISTORY (Requirement 5)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Place an order (Idempotency-Key prevents duplicates on retry)
# @name placeOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Idempotency-Key: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingAddress": {
    "line1": "12 Wankhede Road",
    "city": "Mumbai",
    "state": "Maharashtra",
    "postalCode": "400020",
    "country": "India"
  },
  "paymentMethod": 3,
  "couponCode": "WELCOME10"
}

### Order history (paginated, filterable by status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Order details by number
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORD-2026-000001
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### Cancel an order (restores stock)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORD-2026-000001/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "reason": "Changed my mind" }

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### ADMIN — Product management (Admin role required)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a product with variants
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MI Limited Edition Hoodie",
  "description": "Premium Mumbai Indians hoodie.",
  "type": 5,
  "franchiseId": "REPLACE-WITH-FRANCHISE-ID",
  "basePrice": 2499,
  "imageUrl": null,
  "variants": [
    { "sku": "MI-HOODIE-M", "size": "M", "color": "Blue", "stock": 25, "priceOverride": null }
  ]
}

### Update a product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/REPLACE-WITH-PRODUCT-ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "REPLACE-WITH-PRODUCT-ID",
  "name": "MI Limited Edition Hoodie (2026)",
  "description": "Updated description.",
  "basePrice": 2299,
  "imageUrl": null
}

### Soft-delete a product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/REPLACE-WITH-PRODUCT-ID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### BONUS — Coupons, Reviews, Wishlist
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Validate a coupon (public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupons/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "WELCOME10", "cartTotal": 2000 }

### Create a coupon (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "IPL25",
  "type": 1,
  "value": 25,
  "minOrderValue": 1000,
  "maxDiscount": 750,
  "expiresAtUtc": "2027-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "usageLimit": 500
}

### List coupons (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Add a review (must be a verified buyer of the product)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/REPLACE-WITH-PRODUCT-ID/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "rating": 5, "title": "Top quality", "body": "Authentic and comfortable." }

### List product reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/REPLACE-WITH-PRODUCT-ID/reviews

### Wishlist — add / list / remove
POST {{baseUrl}}/wishlist/REPLACE-WITH-PRODUCT-ID
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/wishlist
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

###
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/wishlist/REPLACE-WITH-PRODUCT-ID
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### HEALTH
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET http://localhost:5080/health/ready
